{"tid":980479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：特朗普建議第二次美朝峰會下月越南舉行","createTime":"2019-01-13T14:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T14:11:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"591d47f9d317157ae540796987c135700960c6fb","tid":980479,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190113/s00005/c98387dea8097eb2c522bf60ff9662de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190113%2Fs00005%2Fc98387dea8097eb2c522bf60ff9662de.jpg&h=7a9943c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普與朝鮮領袖金正恩的第二次峰會，或有機會於越南舉行。日媒報道，特朗普向朝鮮一方提議，2月中旬在越南舉行會談，朝鮮暫未作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩發表新年演說時，表示願意與特朗普隨時再次會面，但警告美國若繼續對朝鮮施壓和制裁，朝鮮可能另開一條「新路」。特朗普早前稱收到金正恩信件，將在「不太遙遠的未來」與金正恩會晤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190113/s00005/1547385488098/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%9D%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190113%2Fs00005%2F1547385488098%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%259C%259D%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C&d=DZ5DvETT3vwd8qf6e%2By6ix4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=ac3c66f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190113%2Fs00005%2F1547385488098%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%259C%259D%25E5%25B3%25B0%2